longBusinessSummary: Bioextrax AB (publ) develops and commercializes a bio-based extraction platform technology. It harvests bioplastics (PHA) granules, organic hydrolyzed protein, keratin fibers, bio-oils, protein-rich by products, and amino acids from bacteria. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Lund, Sweden.
